Description: SpatMCDA is an R package designed for spatial multi-criteria decision analysis,
    providing tools and functions to aid in the assessment and visualization of infectious
    disease risks, especially in data-scarce environments. It leverages advanced spatial data
    analysis techniques to enable robust decision-making.
